==标志==
人权战线的官方标志在1995年启用，是一个蓝色方框中有一个黄色平等标志。这个标志在1995年由设计公司Stone Yamashita设计，时任执行董事伊丽莎白·伯奇被这款设计吸引。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.hrc.org/the-hrc-story/about-our-logo|title = About Our Logo|publisher = Human Rights Campaign|accessdate = 2015-06-19|archive-date = 2015-11-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151112082857/http://www.hrc.org/the-hrc-story/about-our-logo|dead-url = no}}</ref>人权战线（当时是人权战线基金）之前的标志是程式化的燃烧着的火炬。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://rmc.library.cornell.edu/HRC/exhibition/images/570pxw/REX023_091.jpg|title = Old HRCF logo on lapel|publisher = Cornell University|accessdate = 2015-06-19|archive-date = 2020-09-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200917174840/https://rmc.library.cornell.edu/HRC/exhibition/images/570pxw/REX023_091.jpg|dead-url = no}}</ref> 人权战线把印有他们的标志的旗子叫做“平等之旗”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://shop.hrc.org/hrc-equality-flag.html/ |title=HRC Store page selling ''Equality Flag'' |accessdate=2015-06-19 |archive-date=2020-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231233528/https://shop.hrc.org/hrc-equality-flag.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===婚姻平等标志===
[[File:Hrc_logo_red.svg|thumb]]的支持。]] 
人权战线的平等标志用红色填充，来表示支持[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]。红色意味着爱情，人权战线与2013年3月25日在[[社交网络|社交网络]]上分享了他们的标志的红色版本，要求支持者们转发分享，支持婚姻平等。当时[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]正在审理两个案件：[[美国诉温莎案|美国诉温莎案]]和{{link-en|霍林斯沃斯诉佩里|Hollingsworth v. Perry}}案。这个标志如病毒般扩散，仅在3月26日，[[Facebook|Facebook]]上将资料照片更换为平等标志的用户增长了120%。名人如[[乔治·武井|乔治·武井]]、[[碧昂斯|碧昂斯]]、[[索菲亚·布什|索菲亚·布什]]、{{link-en|帕德玛·拉克施密|Padma Lakshmi}}、[[玛莎·斯图尔特|玛莎·斯图尔特]]、[[麦可莫|麦可莫]]、[[莱恩·路易斯|莱恩·路易斯]]和[[艾伦·德杰尼勒斯|艾伦·德杰尼勒斯]]都与他们上百万的粉丝在社交网络上分享了这个标志，还有政治家如参议员[[克莱尔·麦卡斯基尔|克莱尔·麦卡斯基尔]]、[[杰伊·洛克菲勒|杰伊·洛克菲勒]]和{{link-en|凯·黑根|Kay Hagan}}也做了同样的事。<ref>{{cite news|last=Thielman|first=Sam|title=DOMA Nation: The Human Rights Campaign had no idea this was going to happen|url=http://www.adweek.com/news/advertising-branding/doma-nation-148206|accessdate=2013-06-09|newspaper=[[Adweek|Adweek]]|date=2013-03-28|archive-date=2016-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161128044856/http://www.adweek.com/news/advertising-branding/doma-nation-148206|dead-url=no}}</ref>

正当这个标志流行之时，无数的模因被创造。高知名度的品牌和大公司通过对人权战线标志的创意再现展示了他们对于婚姻平等的支持。这些支持者包括{{link-en|Bud Light|Bud Light}}、[[Bonobos|Bonobos]]、{{link-en|fab.com|fab.com}}、{{link-en|凯尼斯·柯尔|Kenneth Cole}}、[[欧舒丹|欧舒丹]]、[[美宝莲|美宝莲]]、[[绝对伏特加|绝对伏特加]]、[[马克·雅各布斯|马克·雅各布斯]]、[[斯米诺伏特加|斯米诺伏特加]]、{{link-en|Martha Stewart Weddings|Martha Stewart Weddings}}和[[HBO|HBO]]的[[真爱如血|真爱如血]]。<ref>{{cite news|last=Brettman|first=Allan|title=From Nike to marriage equality, controversy can be a good thing|url=http://www.oregonlive.com/playbooks-profits/index.ssf/2013/03/from_nike_to_marriage_equality.html|accessdate=2013-06-09|newspaper=[[The_Oregonian|The Oregonian]]|date=2013-03-30|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612141643/http://www.oregonlive.com/playbooks-profits/index.ssf/2013/03/from_nike_to_marriage_equality.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

主要纸媒和网络媒体报道了这项疯狂流行运动的成功，包括[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Maresca|first=Cara|title=Seeing red: Symbol for marriage equality goes viral|url=http://tv.msnbc.com/2013/03/26/seeing-red-human-rights-campaigns-marriage-equality-logo-goes-viral|publisher=MSNBC|accessdate=2013-04-18|archive-date=2013-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130805195216/http://tv.msnbc.com/2013/03/26/seeing-red-human-rights-campaigns-marriage-equality-logo-goes-viral/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 、《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》<ref>{{cite news|last=Yang|first=Mackenzie|title=What Is the Red Equal Sign All Over Facebook and Twitter?|url=http://newsfeed.time.com/2013/03/26/what-is-the-red-equal-sign-all-over-facebook-and-twitter/|accessdate=2013-04-18|work=Time|date=2013-03-26|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207005211/https://newsfeed.time.com/2013/03/26/what-is-the-red-equal-sign-all-over-facebook-and-twitter/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[Mashable|Mashable]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Fox|first=Zoe|title=Facebook Turns Red as SCOTUS Marriage Equality Hearings Begin|url=http://mashable.com/2013/03/26/facebook-red-marriage-equality/|accessdate=2013-04-18|archive-date=2020-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007233227/https://mashable.com/2013/03/26/facebook-red-marriage-equality/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》<ref>{{cite news|last=Neal|first=Mann|title=Gay-Marriage Symbol Goes Viral|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/washwire/2013/03/26/gay-marriage-symbol-goes-viral/?mod=e2tw|publisher=The Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2013-04-18|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917143902/https://blogs.wsj.com/washwire/2013/03/26/gay-marriage-symbol-goes-viral/?mod=e2tw|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

