==批评==
针对人权战线的批评主要是偏爱[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]。<ref>Sullivan, Andrew. (February 19, 2007) [http://andrewsullivan.theatlantic.com/the_daily_dish/2007/02/the_human_right.html The Human Rights Campaign (Blech)] {{Wayback|url=http://andrewsullivan.theatlantic.com/the_daily_dish/2007/02/the_human_right.html |date=20110201094657 }} ''[[The_Atlantic_Monthly|The Atlantic Monthly]]''. Retrieved July 29, 2007.</ref><ref>Sullivan, Andrew. "My Alliance with the Christianists" [http://andrewsullivan.theatlantic.com/the_daily_dish/2007/03/my_alliance_wit.html Theatlantic.com] {{Wayback|url=http://andrewsullivan.theatlantic.com/the_daily_dish/2007/03/my_alliance_wit.html |date=20110130072334 }}</ref>{{link-en|安德鲁·苏利文|Andrew Sullivan}}是一名同性恋政治专栏作家和博客写手，曾批评人权战线为“民主党的赞助翅膀”。该组织回应说：“没有人比{{link-en|托尼·伯金斯|Tony Perkins}}和{{link-en|詹姆斯·杜布森|James Dobson}}更高兴安德鲁·苏利文在做什么了。”这两个人是LGBT社群中{{link-en|社会保守主义|Social conservatism in the United States}}的领导者，也是直率的批评者。<ref name="tony perkins">{{cite news|last=Perkins|first=Tony|title=Christian compassion requires the truth about harms of homosexuality|url=http://onfaith.washingtonpost.com/onfaith/guestvoices/2010/10/christian_compassion_requires_the_truth_about_harms_of_homosexuality.html|accessdate=2012-02-22|newspaper=The Washington Post|date=2010-10-11|archive-date=2013-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723053513/http://onfaith.washingtonpost.com/onfaith/guestvoices/2010/10/christian_compassion_requires_the_truth_about_harms_of_homosexuality.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=dodson>{{cite web|last=Dodson|first=James|title=Marriage Under Fire (excerpt)|url=http://www.christianbookpreviews.com/christian-book-excerpt.php?isbn=1590524314|accessdate=2012-02-22|archive-date=2020-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200323184547/http://www.christianbookpreviews.com/christian-book-excerpt.php?isbn=1590524314|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://groups.yahoo.com/group/transgendernews/message/19553 HRC hits back at blogger criticisms – Washington Blade] {{Wayback|url=http://groups.yahoo.com/group/transgendernews/message/19553 |date=20121101231652 }} originally [http://www.washblade.com/2007/3-16/news/national/10212.cfm here] {{Wayback|url=http://www.washblade.com/2007/3-16/news/national/10212.cfm |date=20080205171919 }}</ref>

人权战线在1998年纽约市共和党员{{link-en|Al D'Amato|Al D'Amato}}的参议院议员连任竞选时的代言，招致了更多地批评。人权战线解释说他对于《禁止就业歧视法案》的通过和“不问，不说”法律的废除表示支持。然而，很多开明的LGBT领导人并不欢迎他的保守姿态，包括他对于[[平权法案|平权法案]]和[[堕胎|堕胎]]的反对。<ref>Kaiser, Charles. (July 18, 2000) [http://books.google.com/books?id=Z2MEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA72&lpg=PA72&dq=Kaiser,+Charles.+%2818+July+2000%29+d%27amato+factor+advocate&source=bl&ots=9326I-yZy0&sig=TsN9ngxvE96oRZHCIcpvAux3A6A&hl=en&sa=X&ei=Qo1ET_bAL-u00QG28e2eBA&ved=0CEkQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q=Kaiser%2C%20Charles.%20%2818%20July%202000%29%20d%27amato%20factor%20advocate&f=false The D'Amato Factor] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Z2MEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA72&lpg=PA72&dq=Kaiser,+Charles.+%2818+July+2000%29+d%27amato+factor+advocate&source=bl&ots=9326I-yZy0&sig=TsN9ngxvE96oRZHCIcpvAux3A6A&hl=en&sa=X&ei=Qo1ET_bAL-u00QG28e2eBA&ved=0CEkQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q=Kaiser%2C%20Charles.%20%2818%20July%202000%29%20d%27amato%20factor%20advocate&f=false |date=20140907221410 }} ''[[The_Advocate|The Advocate]]''. Retrieved February 22, 2012.</ref>

人权战线也因为夸大了成员数量以增加政治影响力而被指责。<ref name="Cookbook">{{Cite web |url=http://citizenchris.typepad.com/citizenchris/2007/03/the_nations_lar.html |title=Citizen Crain: Cooking the books at HRC |accessdate=2015-06-19 |archive-date=2011-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111013192751/http://citizenchris.typepad.com/citizenchris/2007/03/the_nations_lar.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://andrewsullivan.theatlantic.com/the_daily_dish/2007/03/hrc_responds_1.html |title=The Daily Dish {{!}} By Andrew Sullivan |accessdate=2015-06-19 |archive-date=2011-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110130072339/http://andrewsullivan.theatlantic.com/the_daily_dish/2007/03/hrc_responds_1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 人权战线前主席乔·索尔蒙内赛回应称，“成员资格不只是做贡献……还有发送邮件给一些官员，志愿服务的时间或游说国会成员”，而且超过半数的成员在过去两年中做出了贡献。<ref name="$1">[http://www.cross-nation.com/dnf-092008-hrcnumbersgame.html HRC 'members' include all who ever donated $1 – Washington Blade] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cross-nation.com/dnf-092008-hrcnumbersgame.html |date=20120715035410 }} originally [http://washingtonblade.com/2005/5-6/news/national/members.cfm here] {{Wayback|url=http://washingtonblade.com/2005/5-6/news/national/members.cfm |date=20080907170419 }}</ref> 早些时候，人权战线发言人史蒂文·费希尔表示成员资格包括任何捐献过1美元以上的人。<ref name="$1"/>

一些[[跨性别|跨性别]]人士批评人权战线对于《禁止就业歧视法案》的2007年版本的姿态。这个版本把性取向列为被保护的类别，但排除了[[性别认同|性别认同]]和[[性别_(文化)|性别表达]]。<ref>Schindler, Paul. (October 4, 2007) [http://www.gaycitynews.com/site/news.cfm?newsid=18883568&BRD=2729&PAG=461&dept_id=568864&rfi=6 HRC Alone in Eschewing No-Compromise Stand] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gaycitynews.com/site/news.cfm?newsid=18883568&BRD=2729&PAG=461&dept_id=568864&rfi=6 |date=20080409024947 }} Gay City News. Retrieved October 8, 2007.</ref>当共和党员[[巴尼·弗兰克|巴尼·弗兰克]]提交法案时，人权战线没有正式地批评或反对。<ref name=rose>{{Cite news|url=http://www.advocate.com/news_detail_ektid49565.asp|title=Donna Rose on Why She Resigned as the Only Transgender Member of HRC's Board|date=2007-10-04|accessdate=2013-04-02|publisher=[[The_Advocate|The Advocate]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919202932/http://www.advocate.com/news_detail_ektid49565.asp|archivedate=2008-09-19}}</ref> 此后人权战线前主席乔·索尔蒙内赛在跨性别人士“{{link-en|南方安慰大会|South Comfort Conference}}”上说，人权战线“反对任何不完全包含的法案”。<ref name=solomonese>{{Cite news|url=http://www.edgesanfrancisco.com/index.php?ch=news&sc=glbt&sc2=features&sc3=&id=77775|title=HRC's ENDA dilemma: Dine, party or boycott?|date=2008-07-22|accessdate=2011-03-25|publisher=EDGE Publications, Inc.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130121202635/http://www.edgesanfrancisco.com/index.php?ch=news&sc=glbt&sc2=features&sc3=&id=77775|archivedate=2013-01-21}}</ref> 人权战线之后解释说它不能积极地支持一个不完全包含的法案，但是也不反对，因为这项法案会在策略上从长远推动通过包括跨性别人士的《禁止就业歧视法案》。<ref>{{cite web|last=Sandeen|first=Autumn|title=ENDA Passed Without "Real Or Perceived Gender" Protections|url=http://pamshouseblend.firedoglake.com/2007/11/07/enda-passed-without-real-or-perceived-gender-protections/|publisher=pamhouseblend.com|accessdate=2012-02-22|archive-date=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702201158/http://pamshouseblend.firedoglake.com/2007/11/07/enda-passed-without-real-or-perceived-gender-protections/|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，在一封致[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]的信中，人权战线表达了对法案的支持，表示人权战线尽管“对《禁止就业歧视法案》的现有版本极为失望……我们感激我们的同盟的……坚定的支持……哪怕当他们被迫……做出以尺衡量而不是以丈衡量的进步。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pamspaulding.com/graphics/LCCR_ENDA_%20Letter.pdf |title="Letter to U.S. Representatives" |accessdate=2015-06-19 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924063629/http://www.pamspaulding.com/graphics/LCCR_ENDA_%20Letter.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年，长期的婚姻平等活动家{{link-en|沈娜·贝洛斯|Shenna Bellows}}被提名为代表缅因州的美国参议院议员。人权战线支持了她的对手，在职的共和党参议员[[苏珊·科林斯|苏珊·科林斯]]，是一个此前没有支持婚姻平等的议员。不过，克里斯之后澄清了她的观点，支持LGBT婚姻平等。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/06/25/susan-collins-human-rights-campaign_n_5530867.html |title="Susan Collins Endorsed By Major Gay Rights Group, Despite Not Backing Marriage Equality" |accessdate=2015-06-19 |archive-date=2019-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209165107/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/06/25/susan-collins-human-rights-campaign_n_5530867.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

